title: For Sale/Trade:  Custom 1911 (Ed Brown, EGW Trigger, Vanguard, Etc)
postcontent:
I've owned many 1911's in my day. Everything from Para to Wilson, but this 1911 has got to be the greatest one I've owned. I took a Norinco government frame and slide (made from recycled railroad rails, some of the hardest steel in the world), gutted most everything, replaced with Ed Brown internals, and a EGW Trigger group. Had all the work done by Vanguard Custom and then had a hard chrome finish put on it. This thing will group like my Wilson, and could out last my military Colt. I wanted something that would go bang if it was under water, filled with sand, packed with mud, and then just wipe down without chemicals (That wasn't a Glock)...and this is IT. I've only put about 300rds through it in the time I've had it. It has mainly stayed in the safe. I'm open to trades for other firearms or firearm/optic combos.

postcontent:
I have a customized Romanian PSL Paratrooper I am looking to sell. It is a great shooting gun with Low round count (300 +/-). It is in excellent condition but looking to get a 7.62 NATO caliber.  This rifle also has the bolt hold-open mechanism that is on the true military spec PSL rifles that US commercial-spec PSL rifles often omit. 
MFG:  SC Fabrica de Arme Cugir SA (ARMS arsenal)

It is chambered in 7.62X54R (Russian) features a 18 1/8” barrel overall w/ flash suppressor welded. I have performed a reverse rivet process where all the rivets are welded flush into the receiver. The safety has an extended finger latch so you can easily activate/deactivate it. The PSL also has a Harris Bipod and 2 MOE Magpul rail sections attached to the sides of the hand guards.

All furniture is wood but I have refinished to make it look like synthetic. It also has a side mount weaver rail and includes a BSA Mil-Dot 6-24X40 scope w/ rings. BSA is not a very high quality brand but it matches the gun. It is always good to have an extra scope lying around too. The PSL is coated with Cerakote in Coyote Tan and Magpul Foliage Green™. I will do a lifetime warranty on the Cerakote application. PSL has 2 mags.

I also have 1000 +/- 100 or so rounds (not sure how many) of 7.62X54R Steel Core Penetrator (silver tip) non corrosive w/ Ammo cans and I have a black gun case I’ll include on a full price offer. Gun only is $1350 OBO

Please feel free to contact me anytime. I prefer to do a Private Party xfer FTF & must show CO ID. However, I do not mind letting a dealer who is close do it if that is the route buyer prefers. Please feel free to contact me with any questions or if you would like more pictures.

Kevin
